OL,3,CGuernsey water bills to increase in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FGuernsey Water has announced its bills
OL,7,Fwill increase from Wednesday 1 January.
OL,9,FTypical household water bills are set
OL,10,Fto rise between #5 and #8 - an 11%
OL,11,Fincrease for metered customers and 12%
OL,12,Ffor unmetered customers.
OL,14,FGuernsey Water managing director,
OL,15,FSteve Langlois, says they have seen
OL,16,F"significantly higher costs" in the
OL,17,Flast two years as they invest in the
OL,18,Fisland's water network.
