OL,3,CGuernsey water bills to increase in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FThe water company has vowed that any
OL,7,Fincome from the increase will go
OL,8,Ftowards investing in "essential
OL,9,Fservices".
OL,11,FGuernsey Water is investing #2.8
OL,12,Fmillion into new tankers, with further
OL,13,Ffunds going towards the renewal of St
OL,14,FSaviour's water treatment works.
OL,16,FA further #6.4 million will go towards
OL,17,Fdeveloping the Island's water network
OL,18,Fand other infrastructure, including a
OL,19,Fcontinuation of the water ring main
OL,20,Freplacement.
