OL,3,CGuernsey water bills to increase in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FMr Langlois explains: "It has taken
OL,7,Fover 100 years to develop these
OL,8,Ffacilities and they require continuous
OL,9,Finvestment to maintain and renew them,
OL,10,Fand for reasons that are out of our
OL,11,Fcontrol the cost of doing this has
OL,12,Fincreased considerably.
OL,14,F"These assets have served our
OL,15,Fcommunity for generations, and their
OL,16,Frenovation will ensure they continue
OL,17,Fdelivering for decades to come."
