OL,3,CGuernsey water bills to increase in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FThere will also be an increase to the
OL,7,Fcesspit emptying charge from #9.09 per
OL,8,Fload to #10.47, affecting
OL,9,Fapproximately 5,500 islanders.
OL,11,FGuernsey Water says they are working
OL,12,Fto reduce costs, saving #325,000 in
OL,13,F2023 through changing how they
OL,14,Fmaintain wastewater assets.
OL,16,FHowever, the water company added that
OL,17,Fthey were "unable to avoid putting
OL,18,Fcharges up".
